# Production build (Vercel). Use a RELATIVE API base so the browser calls the
# frontend's own origin, and Vercel's /api/* rewrite (see vercel.json) proxies
# it to the backend. This keeps requests same-origin, which is required by the
# strict production CSP (connect-src 'self'). Do NOT point this directly at the
# Railway URL — that would be cross-origin and get blocked by CSP.
VITE_API_URL=/api/v1
